input_analysis.raw_prompt:
"You represent a retail bank in the Netherlands called Acme Bank.  You have decided to reduce the loan application of applicants from one day to less than ten minutes for 95% of the cases as a target.  For this your team outsources the development of an AI model to accept or reject loan applications to a company in Canada.  The company in Canada develops an AI model in close collaboration with your team in the Netherlands utilizes your company’s provided custom data for development of the AI model. Once completed,  your team hosts the AI driven system in a data center in Poland and uses this AI model to decide loan applications for customers who apply for credit to Acme bank.   In this what is your role according to the EU AI Act?
"
